name: textobj-jabraces
description:
*textobj-jabraces* is a Vim plugin to provide text objects for Japanese braces
such as 「...」 and 【...】.


Requirements:
- Vim 7.0 or later
- |textobj-user| 0.3.3 or later (vimscript#2100)

Latest version:
http://github.com/kana/vim-textobj-jabraces

Document in HTML format:
http://kana.github.com/config/vim/textobj-jabraces.html
